name: Gatefold Folder Mount 12x8
description:
<B>Spicer Hallfield Slip-In Gatefold Folder Mount</B>

Spicer Hallfield Carnival A4 (12 x 8) Slip-In Gatefold Mount. Each mount is made from Black heavyweight board with a single tone double-mount effect. The overall size of each gatefold mount is 14"x11" with an A4 aperture suited for 12x8 (30.5cm x 20.3cm) prints. These mounts can be used in either portrait or landscape format.

Can be slipped into a frame or stand alone. Makes an excellent presentation mount for your purchased print.

No gum tape, glue or fastenings necessary simply slip your purchased print into the mount.

Please see the FAQ section for more information on our Mounting policies.

Print not included, please see the store for a wide variety of fine art prints to purchase along with your gatefold folder mount.

All purchases will be delivered to you in a board-backed padded envelope to keep your purchase in perfect condition. To save you money we will combine shipping on multiple orders so you pay less for delivery.

Postage is free for this item when purchased with a print
